txt.en: The store house can be found in Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should deliver the empty crates to the store house in Trestlebridge.
Deliver the empty crates to the store house in Trestlebridge
Cad Buckthorn can be found in Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should talk to Cad Buckthorn.
The crates have been successfully delivered!
'Thank you! This helps us a great deal! The Woodcutter's Brotherhood is grateful for your assistance, [placeholder].'

'As you can see, the reconstruction efforts here in Trestlebridge have left the village in a bit of a mess. There are a lot of empty crates left all over the village.\n\n'Would you mind picking up the empty crates and delivering them to the store house? If you assist us, then we will be able to load up the crates with more supplies and speed up our reconstruction efforts.'
Constant attacks have left Trestlebridge in disrepair, and the Woodcutter's Brotherhood are doing everything they can to restore the village.
Empty crates can be found throughout Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should collect all the empty crates.
